name: Gazebo Strategy Plugin
body:
## Welcome to the GitHub webpage of The Gazebo Strategy Plugin (RTS HSI)

If you want to download the different prototypes, please proceed to the release section ([releases](https://github.com/m4k2k/Gazebo_Strategy_Plugin/releases))

The Gazebo Strategy Plugin is an implementation of the Real Time Strategy based Human-Swarm Interaction (RTS HSI) technique using ROS and Gazebo.

The project is the result of an MSc dissertation project.
